{"meta":{"title":"Moroni 2","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2?lang=deu","contentType":"text/html","pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"6a682a3f5eff55333b750b3467695264f6965bd2","data-aid":"114237315","data-aid-version":"4","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2","lang":"deu","data-orig-id":"c528b9ff04433774f8e0ccd008b533bfe32b89cb","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Moroni 2","description":"Jesus gab den zwölf nephitischen Jüngern Macht, die Gabe des Heiligen Geistes zu übertragen. Um 401–421 n. Chr."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Moroni 2","description":"Jesus gab den zwölf nephitischen Jüngern Macht, die Gabe des Heiligen Geistes zu übertragen. Um 401–421 n. Chr."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"142120644\" id=\"title_number1\">Kapitel 2</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"114237318\" id=\"study_summary1\">Jesus gab den zwölf nephitischen Jüngern Macht, die Gabe des Heiligen Geistes zu übertragen. Um 401–421 n. Chr.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237319\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Die Worte Christi, die er zu seinen <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Jüngern</a> sprach, den Zwölf, die er erwählt hatte, als er ihnen die Hände auflegte –</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237320\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>und er nannte sie beim Namen und sprach: Ihr sollt den Vater in meinem Namen anrufen in mächtigem Gebet; und nachdem ihr dies getan habt, werdet ihr <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Macht</a> haben, denjenigen, denen ihr die <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>Hände</a> auflegt, den <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>Heiligen</a> Geist zu spenden; und in meinem Namen sollt ihr ihn spenden, denn so tun es meine Apostel.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"114237321\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Nun sprach Christus diese Worte zu ihnen zur Zeit seines ersten Erscheinens; und die Menge hörte es nicht, sondern die Jünger hörten es; und auf alle, denen sie die Hände <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>auflegten</a>, fiel der Heilige Geist.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237322\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/13.25?lang=deu#p25\">3 Ne 13:25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237323\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/power?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Macht</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237324\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/hands-laying-on-of?lang=deu\"><small>SF</small> Hände, Auflegen der</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note2c\" data-full-marker=\"2c\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237325\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.37?lang=deu#p37\">3 Ne 18:37</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"114237326\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/acts/19.6?lang=deu#p6\">Apg 19:6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"p1":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"Die Gabe des Heiligen Geistes","aspectRatio":"0.6666666666666666","height":"480","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/45/b8/45b82cd654d20eb44f4cf443d1fa3579aaf73212/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/11/d2/11d2be5412ff4da00064b0aafa623543f4a33c40/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/35/08/35089306a99a1a2ab76ca53d06901937a867f6ee/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/6c/e8/6ce85734371a445c93d5122dfa82803d2acd2a15/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 250w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/58/c7/58c7a81027d5dc120e539da690f7e25c4c5809b4/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 320w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/26/1f/261f2b4e9f5b75066cfa5c39057e94325460e27a/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 500w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/37/e5/37e59429886368b873cce4c15e1e7367852e0d36/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 640w","imgId":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","src":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/58/c7/58c7a81027d5dc120e539da690f7e25c4c5809b4/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg","id":"aside1_img1","altSource":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/media/image/girl-being-confirmed-8e69acd","attribs":{"data-alt-source":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/media/image/girl-being-confirmed-8e69acd","id":"aside1_img1","src":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/58/c7/58c7a81027d5dc120e539da690f7e25c4c5809b4/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg","data-img-id":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/45/b8/45b82cd654d20eb44f4cf443d1fa3579aaf73212/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/11/d2/11d2be5412ff4da00064b0aafa623543f4a33c40/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/35/08/35089306a99a1a2ab76ca53d06901937a867f6ee/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/6c/e8/6ce85734371a445c93d5122dfa82803d2acd2a15/girl_being_c